Description: PyJSONViewer
        ============
        
        A JSON file data viewer using pure python
        
        -  Mac OS
        
        .. figure:: https://github.com/AtsushiSakai/PyJSONViewer/raw/master/img/mac.png
           :alt: img1
        
           img1
        
        -  Windows10
        
